<a name="accommodation">
  <h2>Accommodation</h2>
  The city center of Antwerp boasts a large number of good
  hotels.  For convenience of transportation, take a hotel close
  to the central station.  Some hotels very close to the central
  station are the Tourist**, the Florida***, the Empire***, the
  Agora***, and the Atlanta***.  You can find all of them on <a
    href="http://hotels.com">hotels.com</a>.
  <p>
  One good hotel we can personally recommend for its friendly
  staff, it is 500 meters from the central station, is
  <a href="http://www.colombushotel.com">Hotel Colombus</a>.
  They give a special price for university
  guests; at check-in or check-out, just tell them you are
  visiting the university and they will give you a hefty discount.
  <p>
  Another hotel we can specially recommend, although it is not
  close to the central station, is <a
    href="http://www.elzenveld.be">Hotel Elzenveld</a>, for its
  wonderful building, atmosphere and location in the city center.
  They also give a special price for university guests.
  Moreover, you can easily take tram&nbsp;7 in front of this
  hotel and get off at the same stop "Koninklijkelaan" as that of
  tram&nbsp;15 mentioned above.
  <p>
  For the young or budget-conscious traveler, there is also a great
<a href="http://www.vjh.be">youth hostel in
  Antwerp</a> belonging to the Hosteling International quality
chain of hostels.  
